Package com.alcatel_lucent.nz.wnmsextract.database.rnccn Description

RncCn is a top level package mapping the WNMS RncCn component. Its structure is simple but densely packed with UtranCell containing the majority of the cell level data used in the application. Its structure is as follows:

RNCFunction
→NeighbouringRnc
→UtranCell
